INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (975,'199900202005','a) Mean no. of children = $$\\frac{total.no.of.children}{total.no.of.families} =\\frac{1\\times 7+2\\times 18+3\\times 11+4\\times 4}{7+18+11+4}=2.3$$;;b-i) Angle representing blue and green = $$360^{\\circ}-90^{\\circ}-110^{\\circ}=160^{\\circ}$$;;Blue : Green = 3 : 1;;Angle representing green = $$\\frac{1}{4} \\times 160^{\\circ}=40^{\\circ}$$;;b-ii) $$110^{\\circ}-90^{\\circ}=20^{\\circ}$$ represents 8 students;;$$110^{\\circ}$$ represents $$\\frac{8}{20^{\\circ}} \\times 110^{\\circ} = 44 students$$;;c-i) P(first child is girl) = $$\\frac{No.of.girls}{No.of.children}=\\frac{12}{12+3}=\\frac{4}{5}$$;;c-ii) P(first child is girl and second is boy) ;;$$=\\frac{4}{5} \\times P(second.child.is.boy)$$;;$$=\\frac{4}{5}\\times\\frac{3}{15-1}$$;;$$=\\frac{6}{35}$$;;c-iii) P(a child of each sex chosen);;=P(first.child.is.girl.and.second.is.boy) + P(first.child.is.boy.and.second.is.girl);;$$=\\frac{6}{35} + P(first.child.is.boy) \\times P(second.child.is.girl)$$;;$$=\\frac{6}{35}+\\frac{3}{15}\\times\\frac{12}{14}$$;;$$=\\frac{6}{35}+\\frac{12}{35}=\\frac{18}{35}$$');
