INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (977,'199900202007','a-i) For rectangle A = $$length \\times width = area$$;;width = $$\\frac{area}{length}=\\frac{11}{x}cm$$;;a-ii) For rectangle B, width = $$\\frac{area}{length}=\\frac{11}{x+3}cm$$;;b) Width of rectangle A = Width of rectangle B + 2;;$$\\frac{11}{x}=\\frac{11}{x+3}+2=\\frac{11+2(x+3)}{x+3}$$;;11(x + 3) = x(11 + 2x + 6);;$$11x + 33 = 2x^2 +17x$$;;$$2x^2 +17x-11x-33=0$$(shown);;c) $$2x^2 +6x-33=0$$;;$$x=\\frac{-b \\pm \\sqrt{b^2 -4ac}}{2a}=\\frac{-6 \\pm \\sqrt{6^2 -4(2)(-33)}}{2(2)}=\\frac{-6 \\pm \\sqrt{300}}{4}$$;;$$x=\\frac{-6+\\sqrt{300}}{4} or x = \\frac{-6-\\sqrt{300}}{4}$$;;x= 2.83 or x = -5.83;;d) x = -5.83 is rejected as length cannot be negative.;;Sub. x = 2.83 into the expression,;;Width of rectangle B = $$\\frac{11}{2.83+3}= 1.89cm$$');
