INSERT INTO `DBManagement_answer` (`id`,`question_id_id`,`content`) VALUES (1601,'201000203023','a) In $$\\Delta $$s ALB and NLD ; $$\\angle ALB = \\angle NLD$$ (vert. opp. $$\\angle$$ s) ; $$\\angle $$BAL = $$\\angle $$DNL (alt. $$\\angle $$s, ND $$\\parallel$$ AB) ; $$\\angle $$ABL = $$\\angle $$NDL (alt. $$\\angle $$s, ND $$\\parallel$$ AB) ; $$\\therefore  \\Delta$$ALB and $$\\Delta $$BLD are similar. (Shown);;b) $$\\Delta $$ABM is similar to $$\\Delta $$NCM;;c) $$\\Delta $$ABD and $$\\Delta $$CDB are congruent.;;d-i) $$\\frac{AB}{ND} = \\frac{BL}{DL} = \\frac{1}{3}$$ ; $$\\Rightarrow \\frac{AB}{CN} = \\frac{1}{2}$$;;d-ii) $$\\frac{Area.of.\\Delta ABL}{Area.of.\\Delta ALD}$$ = $$\\frac{BL}{DL}$$ = $$\\frac{1}{3}$$;;d-iii) $$\\frac{Area.of.\\Delta MLB}{Area.of.\\Delta ALD}$$ = $$(\\frac{LB}{LD})^2$$ = (\\frac{1}{3})^2 ; = $$\\frac{1}{9}$$ ($$\\Delta $$MLB is similar to $$\\Delta $$ALD)');
